{"tid":925799,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【母殺親兒】淹死5歲子再斬頭放膠袋 亞裔媽棄親兒屍於垃圾桶","createTime":"2018-12-03T03:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T06:08:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"be772e3974d9d7f1e8c8f32e0d3cfcb9ec40b759","tid":925799,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:56:28.000Z","msg":"美國德州侯斯頓一名女子涉嫌將5歲兒子淹死後，斬去兒子頭顱後將屍體棄於垃圾桶。<br />\n警方表示，43歲譯音姓劉（Lihui Liu）的女子，上周五懷疑在浴室殘殺兒子後棄屍。丈夫放工回家，劉告訴對方已把兒子趕走，丈夫四處尋找兒子之際，劉最終承認兒子在車房外的垃圾桶內。他發現兒子的屍體及頭顱在垃圾桶內以黑膠袋包住。<br />\n警方接報有斬人案後到劉的寓所調查，在浴室發現兇器，浴缸血迹斑斑。劉當場被捕，承認將兒子淹斃，已被控謀殺。劉與丈夫還育有13歲女兒，未知案發時她是否在屋內。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181203/large/1543795031_d51e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181203%2Flarge%2F1543795031_d51e.jpg&h=bcda3359&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"881b9526ec9998dce6b35226112b322d94a2921f","tid":925799,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:12:46.000Z","msg":"咁撚激<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da71aed1942805e460ca13fcb9fd9f8bfc45fe10","tid":925799,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:12:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"707f3fd5a74de34024bce95f6402ffc70f256e17","tid":925799,"uid":71166,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:13:55.000Z","msg":"畜生係咁㗎啦<br />\n殺自己仔女唔出奇"},{"pid":"e6989ca54febe2bbf8c1f3c3f5927fd366ec04ab","tid":925799,"uid":56467,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:29:27.000Z","msg":"好事就華裔 壞事就亞裔"},{"pid":"28508ec8eb300d969a3e5c4555767c423503a596","tid":925799,"uid":57604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e6989ca54febe2bbf8c1f3c3f5927fd366ec04ab","tid":925799,"uid":56467,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:29:27.000Z","msg":"好事就華裔 壞事就亞裔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:35